{
  "stem": "628.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You can have the Washington Museum, but that ground, when you walk on that ground, you walk on your people's ground, on our people's ground, who never came back, who stayed there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At least, you walk a few miles, maybe a day, maybe a few hours, and you feel-- and you fell the suffering, and you feel the shouting.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this is the important thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it has been that after 55 years-- no, after 50 years, it happened, and that gave me satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't have to thank me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I didn't talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's those six millions who talked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, I had 55 years in me, a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] a piece of stone, which didn't open up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I carried that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All my boys, all the Holocaust survivors, they-- we all carry it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them can't even talk now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now that has been opened up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have given our message.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've given it to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've given it to-- and we are loosening up, and it does us good, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it's a heavy, such a heavy burden we had to carry, all these 50 years in us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know how it happened that I got that strength.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never learned to speak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My six million people, your six million people, your families, your kind, we all-- they say it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are saying it, and let them rest in peace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] [SOBBING] There's no saying that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[DRINKS] This Kaddish, which was said twice, we sang them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I'm happy with the young kids like you, who listen to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have to continue that message.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Israel also and Israel will.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'll tell you something else.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
